# TradeOS Code Owners

## Ownership Model
- **Primary Owner**: the team responsible for the package.
- **Backup Owner**: alternate reviewer for high-risk changes.
- **Review Required**: all changes to these paths require review from Primary or Backup.

## Root & Config
/.github/          @tradeos/infra
/vercel.json       @tradeos/infra
/turbo.json        @tradeos/infra
/docker-compose.yml @tradeos/infra

## Apps
/apps/web/         @tradeos/core-web  # Primary: CTO / Backup: CHRO
/apps/worker/      @tradeos/core-backend # Primary: CTO / Backup: CISO

## Core Packages
/packages/policy-core/   @tradeos/core-security  # Primary: CISO / Backup: CTO
/packages/database/      @tradeos/core-backend   # Primary: CTO / Backup: CISO
